面啲野，畀幾個字/ 句子你讀，問你點解<br />\n自我介紹幾句"},{"pid":"10420c1044f06b8c85586d3dbb5bb42e038fdb86","tid":674993,"uid":2340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9fd835010da1f27a0f60d75df725478240795b8d","tid":674993,"uid":48958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T07:29:36.000Z","msg":"意大利文、阿拉伯文、泰文、俄文：雖然有大學有開course，但喺香港應該已經係比較冷門咁<br />\n葡文喺澳門算唔算熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港就應該算冷門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再冷門啲，瑞典文 荷文 波蘭文 烏克蘭文 馬拉文/印尼文 越南文 緬甸文 土耳其文 尼泊爾文 Hindi/Urdu 希伯來文&hellip;（部份工聯會有得學）<br />\n<br />\nLatin同Ancient Greek工聯會都有學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋有冇人認真學中國大陸啲方言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T16:51:44.000Z","msg":"swedish冷門過阿拉伯文咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5680159bb87e89ff26571e96c6c0b52c80b391c","tid":674993,"uid":167032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T16:51:48.000Z","msg":"Jeg har ikke snakker Norsk <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ded03c268e2395a1c80784c2a0dfe36141a735ff","tid":674993,"uid":167032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5680159bb87e89ff26571e96c6c0b52c80b391c","tid":674993,"uid":167032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T16:51:48.000Z","msg":"Jeg har ikke snakker Norsk <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T16:52:07.000Z","msg":"For a long time"},{"pid":"39b38d911a0a678c630064f1d63ab13513f2573f","tid":674993,"uid":59965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5680159bb87e89ff26571e96c6c0b52c80b391c","tid":674993,"uid":167032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T16:51:48.000Z","msg":"Jeg har ikke snakker Norsk <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clo